events.text:
Gogug and Jugog sent word to me that the Old Kingdom has came back from the dirt.
Our ancestors spoke to us of fables fighting the Old Gods long ago, I'm afraid we're of no equal footing for them.
You've come looking to broker peace between us and you kind.
Send word back to your Kingdom to assist us in pushing back these foul creatures and I'll send word to Khozgrogal.
The Old Gods are relentless, only together we can face them.
